Will you be my deputy
medical director?

47
00:02:26,446 --> 00:02:29,712
Sorry, I don't know why that
sounded like I was asking you to prom.

48
00:02:31,685 --> 00:02:34,245
I'm flattered, of course.

49
00:02:35,722 --> 00:02:38,055
